        <item>
            <title>Smart #5 純電 SUV 8 月 28 登場　越野實力全面提升 + 史上最大部 Smart</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/11/new-smart-5-set-for-august-28-reveal-date/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=new-smart-5-set-for-august-28-reveal-date</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/11/new-smart-5-set-for-august-28-reveal-date/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 05:55:55 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[smart]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Smart #5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Smart SUV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SUV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[純電動車]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[越野車]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1255617</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>講起 Smart 這個牌子，大家第一時間聯想到是其的骰車身，但近日 Smart 宣佈 8 月 28 日將會在澳洲推出的新車 Smart #5， 除了具有越野功能，更是迄今最大部的 Smart。相信這部 Smart #5 將推翻各位車迷對 Smart 的既有印象。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255625" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1920_smartconcept5in-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1920_smartconcept5in-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/1920_smartconcept5in.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 圖片來源：<a href="https://media.smart.com/eu/the-most-versatile-smart-of-all-time-the-smart-concept-5/">Smart</a></p><p>Smart #5 SUV 其外觀設計相當引人注目。與以往的小巧車款不同，Smart #5 採用了方正的車身造型，車長達到 4,705mm、寬 1,920mm、高 1,705mm，擁有較高的車身比例，使其外觀更接近 BMW X3 和 Audi Q5 等傳統 SUV。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255631" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/04smartconcept5inter-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/04smartconcept5inter-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/04smartconcept5inter-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 圖片來源：<a href="https://media.smart.com/eu/the-most-versatile-smart-of-all-time-the-smart-concept-5/">Smart</a></p><p>這輛車的外觀設計強調越野性能，車輛配備了鋁合金護板、防刮塑膠包圍，以及額外裝配的 LED 燈組。雖然量產版將不會配備概念車中的全地形輪胎，同時車身亦不會太離地，但這些細節仍為這款電動 SUV 增添了不少越野味。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255627" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smart5rearoffroad-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smart5rearoffroad-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smart5rearoffroad.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 圖片來源：<a href="https://autos.yahoo.com.tw/%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7smart%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%B2-%E7%B4%94%E9%9B%BB%E4%BC%91%E6%97%85-5%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E9%A3%86%E6%B2%99%E8%B6%8A%E9%87%8E%E8%B6%85%E6%9C%89%E5%9E%8B-041204083.html">CarFun</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255635" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smart5ice-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smart5ice-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smart5ice.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 即使在雪地行駛也沒有難度，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.carwow.co.uk/smart/news/7595/new-smart-5-revealed#gref">CarWow</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255636" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/b64cb814eac626a84df7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/b64cb814eac626a84df7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/b64cb814eac626a84df7.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 涉水亦易如反掌，圖片來源：<a href="https://www.carwow.co.uk/smart/news/7595/new-smart-5-revealed#gref">CarWow</a></p><p>內籠設計方面，Smart #5 延續了品牌一貫的現代感與科技感，內飾採用了優質材質，整體設計簡潔而大方。車內空間相當寬敞。Smart 品牌標誌性的圓形元素貫穿整個內籠設計，與外觀設計相呼應。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255629" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/11smartconcept5inter-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/11smartconcept5inter-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/11smartconcept5inter.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 圖片來源：<a href="https://media.smart.com/eu/the-most-versatile-smart-of-all-time-the-smart-concept-5/">Smart</a></p><p>在中控台與娛樂系統方面，Smart #5 配備了一個巨大的圓形資訊娛樂螢幕，為駕駛者和乘客提供便捷的操作體驗。據英媒《Car Magazine》報道，車內娛樂系統由最新的 AMD 晶片驅動，且搭載了生成式人工智能虛擬助手，能夠根據駕駛者的習慣進行智能化操作。此外，前排乘客座椅還具備「零重力」功能，能夠加熱、降温、按摩，甚至有腿部支撐，讓乘客享受更舒適的駕乘體驗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255628" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smartconcept5interst-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smartconcept5interst-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smartconcept5interst-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 圓形資訊娛樂螢幕，圖片來源：<a href="https://media.smart.com/eu/the-most-versatile-smart-of-all-time-the-smart-concept-5/">Smart</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255634" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240809194239-694x520.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240809194239-694x520.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240809194239.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 前排座椅具備「零重力」功能，圖片來源：<a href="https://media.smart.com/eu/the-most-versatile-smart-of-all-time-the-smart-concept-5/">Smart</a></p><p>據台媒引述中國工信部資料顯示，Smart #5 採用由吉利汽車集團提供的 800V 電子架構，具備極快的充電速度，可在 15 分鐘內將電池從 10% 充至 80%。該車款配有多種動力配置，包括單馬達的後輪驅動版本和雙馬達的四輪驅動版本，動力輸出從 335 匹到 637 匹不等，最高效的配置續航里程可達 549 公里。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255630" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smartconcept5interst-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smartconcept5interst-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smartconcept5interst-1-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>據悉 Smart #5 是一款面向全球市場的車款，而 Smart 將於 8 月 28 日在澳洲進行全球首發，發布全新電動越野 SUV Smart#5。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255632" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smartconcept5interst-2-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smartconcept5interst-2-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smartconcept5interst-2-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255633" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smartconcept5interst-3-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smartconcept5interst-3-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smartconcept5interst-3-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>圖片、資料來源：<a href="https://media.smart.com/eu/the-most-versatile-smart-of-all-time-the-smart-concept-5/">Smart</a>、<a href="https://www.carwow.co.uk/smart/news/7595/new-smart-5-revealed#gref">Car Wow</a>、<a href="https://www.carmagazine.co.uk/car-news/first-official-pictures/smart/5/">Car Magazine</a>、<a href="https://autos.yahoo.com.tw/%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7smart%E4%BE%86%E8%A5%B2-%E7%B4%94%E9%9B%BB%E4%BC%91%E6%97%85-5%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E9%A3%86%E6%B2%99%E8%B6%8A%E9%87%8E%E8%B6%85%E6%9C%89%E5%9E%8B-041204083.html">Car Fun</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/zeekr-009-2/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target=